Package org.eclipse.mosaic.starter.cli

Class MosaicParameters

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.starter.cli.MosaicParameters
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MosaicParameters extends Object implements Serializable
This class holds the values of parameters parsed by the CommandLineParser. Also, all parameters are described here using the CommandLineOption annotation.
